GAP 2: EvaluateTask - Go doesn't evaluate Files field
================================================================

Go EvaluateTask evaluates: Name, Var, Image, Queue, Env, If, Pre, Post, Parallel, CMD, SubJob
Go does NOT evaluate: Description, Workdir, Timeout, Files, GPU, Entrypoint, Sidecars, Each

Rust evaluate_task evaluates ALL fields including Files.

EXPECTED FIX in Go eval.go EvaluateTask():
Add evaluation of Files field:
  // evaluate files
  files := t.Files
  for k, v := range files {
      result, err := EvaluateTemplate(v, c)
      if err != nil {
          return err
      }
      files[k] = result
  }
  t.Files = files

